    <h2>Our Verdict</h2>
    <p>Synthesia delivers on its promise: <strong>professional video without the production headache</strong>. For corporate training, product demos, and multilingual content, it's unmatched. The avatar quality keeps improving, and 130+ languages make it a global content powerhouse.</p>
    <p>It's not perfect — occasional pronunciation quirks and limited customization can be frustrating. But for teams that need to produce videos regularly without a production team, Synthesia is a game-changer.</p>
