    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

    <h3>Is Synthesia free?</h3>
    <p>Synthesia offers a free demo where you can create a short video without signing up. Paid plans start at $30/month.</p>

    <h3>Can I use my own voice with Synthesia?</h3>
    <p>Yes. You can upload a voiceover recording, and Synthesia will sync the avatar's lip movements to your audio. This gives you more control over tone and expression.</p>

    <h3>How many languages does Synthesia support?</h3>
    <p>Synthesia supports 130+ languages and dialects, including major languages and regional variations with localized accents.</p>

    <h3>Can I create a custom avatar of myself?</h3>
    <p>Yes. Synthesia offers custom avatar creation where you record yourself (10–15 minutes) and they create a digital twin. This requires additional cost and consent documentation.</p>

    <h3>Is Synthesia better than HeyGen?</h3>
